   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>(Recto);;Antonius Hermes, freedman of Antonius, 40 years old, manupmitted by the claim of his free status [by Antonius - - - in the tribunal of - - -], prefect of Egypt has paid 20 &lt;denarii&gt; for the 5% tax on manumissions of the Roman people. I, Chalcedonius, slave of our (lords) Augusti, have received (it) from Antonius(?) [- - -];;(Verso of tablet I);;[- - -] Hermes(?) [- - -]</ab>
         </div>
